Interface TableReference

  • All Superinterfaces:
    AttributedObject, Comparable<NamedObject>, ContainedObject<Table>, DatabaseObject, DefinedObject, DependantObject<Table>, DescribedObject, Iterable<ColumnReference>, NamedObject, Serializable, TableConstraint, TypedObject<TableConstraintType>
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    ForeignKey, WeakAssociation

    public interface TableReference
extends NamedObject, AttributedObject, DescribedObject, TableConstraint, Iterable<ColumnReference>
    Represents a foreign-key mapping to a primary key in another table.
